('fal-ai/bytedance/seedance/v1.5/pro/image-to-video', 'Bytedance', 'Generate videos with audio with Seedance 1.5 (supports start & end frame) ', 'image-to-video', 'fal-ai', 0, 'tokens', 'Each 720p 5 second video with audio costs roughly **$0.26**. For other resolutions, 1 million video tokens with audio costs **$2.4**. Without audio, the price is **1.2** per millition tokens. tokens(video)  = (height x width x FPS x duration) / 1024. ', '[{"key":"image_size","label":"Image Size","default":"landscape_16_9","options":["landscape_16_9","portrait_4_3","square"]}]'::jsonb, true),
