('bytedance/seedance-2.0/fast/text-to-video', 'Seedance 2.0 Fast Text to Video', 'ByteDance''s most advanced text-to-video model, fast tier. Lower latency and cost with cinematic output, native audio, multi-shot editing, and director-level camera control.', 'text-to-video', 'fal-ai', 0.2419, 'duration_sec', 'For every second of 720p video you generated, you will be charged **$0.2419/second**. Your request will cost **$0.0112** per 1000 tokens. The number of tokens is given by (height of output video * width of output video * duration * 24) / 1024. ', '[{"key":"image_size","label":"Image Size","default":"landscape_16_9","options":["landscape_16_9","portrait_4_3","square"]}]'::jsonb, true),
